1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY

CVSS v3 7.2
ATTENTION: Exploitable remotely/low attack complexity
Vendor: Siemens
Equipment: SCALANCE M-800/S615 Family
Vulnerabilities: Acceptance of Extraneous Untrusted Data With Trusted Data, OS Command Injection

2. RISK EVALUATION
